TESTS.md
/examples/
docs-content/
website-misalignments-*.md

# ─── Internal planning / strategy notes (never publish) ─────────────────────
*_plan.md
*_briefing.md

# ─── Loose desktop dumps at repo root ──────────────────────────────────────
/Screenshot*.png
/screencapture-*.pdf
/screencapture-*.png

